 <h3>Interface</h3>
	<p>Each Todo item can be dragged to change sorting order by clicking and dragging on the grey bar.</p>
	<p>Clicking on a Todo item will allow for editing the item.</p>
	<p>Multiple Todo items can be in an edit state</p>
	<p>When a Todo item is in edit state clicking anywhere outside the item will auto save</p>
	<p>Sections on right hand side are sortable by clicking and dragging the title. Allows for flexible user preferred layouts</p>
